name: Annap Interactive Solutions Private Limited
tag_list: car, bike, accessories, store, online, ecommerce, india
overview: Annap’s flagship portal Vicky.in has become the mouthpiece of digital auto industry in India and serves 5 million customers every month. Vicky.in contributes for auto section of leading publications such as Hindustan Times, Rediff, Sify, Dainik Bhaskar, Eenadu, Vikadan and OneIndia group portals. Our client list includes all prominent auto manufacturers Tata Motors, Volkswagen, Fiat, Nissan and more. Vickyconnect of vicky.in is the India’s first social networking site for car and bike lovers. Vicky.in/shopping is india’s first largest online store for car and bike accessories
